{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"3amoxlza8d4xi7i41azkvb1","title":"Chat Gpt","desc":"","updated":1699525838994,"created":1699524259819,"custom":{},"fname":"programing.chat-gpt","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"eaedb236c8b830052bc4cf328c7c0dad","links":[],"anchors":{"chatgpt":{"type":"header","text":"ChatGPT?","value":"chatgpt","line":8,"column":0,"depth":2},"text-generative-models":{"type":"header","text":"Text Generative Models","value":"text-generative-models","line":10,"column":0,"depth":3},"intro":{"type":"header","text":"Intro","value":"intro","line":23,"column":0,"depth":3},"what-chatgpt-doing":{"type":"header","text":"What ChatGPT doing","value":"what-chatgpt-doing","line":33,"column":0,"depth":3},"prompts":{"type":"header","text":"Prompts","value":"prompts","line":37,"column":0,"depth":2},"basic-tasks":{"type":"header","text":"Basic tasks","value":"basic-tasks","line":46,"column":0,"depth":2},"risks":{"type":"header","text":"Risks","value":"risks","line":53,"column":0,"depth":2},"tips":{"type":"header","text":"Tips","value":"tips","line":60,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"4qi2z0z9fquupbd651xausx","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"chat-gpt\">Chat Gpt<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#chat-gpt\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"chatgpt\">ChatGPT?<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#chatgpt\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"text-generative-models\">Text Generative Models<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#text-generative-models\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>ML algo to create coherent &#x26; contextually relevant text based on learned patterns</li>\n<li>Predict the next sequence token using <strong>probability</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>=> hallucunation: unexpected or illogical outputs </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Probabilities\n<ul>\n<li>Word to vector</li>\n<li>Context: Vectors for a sequence of words are adjusted -> <strong>contextualized vectors</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Predicting the Next word\n<ul>\n<li>contextualized vectors -> estimate the <strong>likelihood</strong> of what the next word might be</li>\n<li>How to end: \n<ul>\n<li>Readched the end token</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"intro\">Intro<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#intro\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>RLHF: Reinforcement Learning from <strong>Human Feedback</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>collect large datasets -> Supervieed policy</li>\n<li>collect comparision data -> reward model</li>\n<li>policy + reward model -> auto training</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Number of params: \n<ul>\n<li>GPT 3/3.5: 175 B</li>\n<li>GPT 4: 1_000 B</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"what-chatgpt-doing\">What ChatGPT doing<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#what-chatgpt-doing\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Tokenize question -> predict the next words based on probability</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"prompts\">Prompts<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#prompts\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Prompts: instructions &#x26; context passed\n<ul>\n<li>Elements\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Instruction</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Context</strong></li>\n<li>Input data</li>\n<li>Output indicator</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"basic-tasks\">Basic tasks<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#basic-tasks\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Text summarization</li>\n<li>Text generation</li>\n<li>Code generation</li>\n<li>Role playing</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"risks\">Risks<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#risks\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>No reasoning ability: \n<ul>\n<li>GPT 4 reasoning ability >> 3/3.5</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Data/prompt leaking\n<ul>\n<li>Hijak LM's output</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"tips\">Tips<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tips\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>English: larger dataset</li>\n<li>Reasoning\n<ul>\n<li>Alias to common knowing: eat ~ subtract</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Chain-of-thought\n<ul>\n<li>Instructions step by step</li>\n<li>Zero-shot: <strong>let's think step by step</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Self-Consistency\n<ul>\n<li>sample multiple, diverse reasoning paths -> most consisten answer</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>GPT 4: Advanced Data Analysis\n<ul>\n<li>Use code to cover <strong>reasoning skills</strong></li>\n<li>Datasheet, image analysis</li>\n<li>Image generation</li>\n<li>Browser: Browsing data</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"xfkxbponh0sohobo6pual15","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1668137379975,"created":1663481872547,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"cb44915142ec96bef8f764f3dc90389e","links":[],"anchors":{"welcome-to-my-page":{"type":"header","text":"Welcome to my page","value":"welcome-to-my-page","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"contacts":{"type":"header","text":"Contacts","value":"contacts","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"dendron":{"type":"header","text":"Dendron","value":"dendron","line":18,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["u5a2e2vvfn3x7k0shuvmb1b","qw8y69zxn8wr7tzz4gtcrrv","q7qw45jglqwmynary64q67c","6wjqcjgkrpeqtmzb1o8o1q8","3ervbn5we7t8v2l2vwtx847","4qi2z0z9fquupbd651xausx","sencgim78q74o1zuyvy1vz7","ue4oml1si982t3mmbthyxi9","zrogwjgtze8ne5joqpz8ty9","oesia0lbzh03fsoy124ck0k","el3p9zjue6h3b6zsl9oejkt","t5grkmcwvu4nl43igsj4gxz"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"# Welcome to my page\n\n- This is a place where I write my knowledge in both Vietnamese and English.\n- Please feel free to correct me if there is anything not right.\n\n## Contacts\n\n- [Github](https://github.com/thanhpp)\n- [Discord](https://discord.gg/ugNRjFNqjp)\n- [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/in/thanhpp/)\n\n## Dendron\n\n- [Home Page](https://wiki.dendron.so/)"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enab